spanGrp.span: Me, I'm called Unyangi of Gerigwegu
anin qawasch jaft rootigeng gagenan asimjeeg
Me, I'm of the Rotigenga tribe and I've married into the Asimjeeg
Mimi ni wa kabila la Warotigenga nimeolewa na waasimjeega
gil bahati mbay qamn madgwand qabar beeshak
But unfortunately he is not around, he was killed by an elephant
Lakini bahati mbàya sasa hivi hayupo aliuawa na tembo
I'm on my own with my children
Niko peke yangu na watoto wangu
We are just struggling with my children
sasa anin ng'asheeg gicha darugw ab qamn
Now me, what I will say for now
Sasa mimi nitakachosema tu kwa sasa
aa qat sind qamn mad gawurj
Until now, it doesn't resemble (that time) at all
That if you are told something by your mother
Kwamba ukiambiwa neno na mama yako
You know that you were told something
debugas su qamn sijilj ba qamni
Our children that we have given birth to now
If you tell your child you will meet with them
gawurjeew gil siy gwach gol qomuqnoony
It is like they already waited for your for a long time
I don't know what it is
In the old days we were also girls
aa much gwanaw qareemang aa qwaheedeeny qamayang'
Another day the boys were looking for you and then mom wakes you up
Siku nyingine vijana wanakufuata halafu mama anakuamsha
And these days children they aren't woken up
Na watoto huwa hawaamshwi kwa sasa
debug ga qamn da much gilas gew aa jaft aa
Children of today you are often surprised, a child
Watoto wa kisasa huwa unashtuka mtoto
qowu siid galeed aa gadgwand shule
She has become a person with a stomach when she is still in school
Amekuwa mtu wa tumbo wakati bado yupo shuleni
I don't know what it is that has bothered her
aa geyonng'wak su qorany ba qamnan
And these diseases now that are increasing
Na hayo magonjwa wa sasa yalivyozidi
I don't know which path we should take
The life that we see now is bad
And now we have six years
gwacheed ar sarakal qany qang'l ar ng'asheeg su ba beahakan qany qaweedees
Even if the government gave us an elephant tusk it would help
Ingekuwa hata serikali wangetupia jicho suala la tembo watusaidie
Our life is really bad now
Maisha yetu ni mbaya sana kwa sasa
onung' ekulesiin ar serekal qahany qany qaweedees
Let's make noise so that the government helps us
Even our children they should be sent for instruction
